sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as React SPA
    participant Backend as FastAPI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Enter credentials
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/register
    Backend->>DB: INSERT users
    DB-->>Backend: user row
    Backend-->>Frontend: access_token + refresh_token

    User->>Frontend: Login
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/login
    Backend->>DB: SELECT users
    DB-->>Backend: user row (password_hash)
    Backend-->>Frontend: JWT access + refresh tokens

    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/v1/auth/refresh
    Backend-->>Frontend: new access_token

    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/logout
    Backend->>DB: DELETE refresh_token
    Backend-->>Frontend: 204 No Content

    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/admin/users (owner)
    Backend->>DB: INSERT invite_token
    DB-->>Backend: token row
    Backend-->>Frontend: Data Owner provisioned
